      "acceptanceCriteria": "Predicted hemolysis index values agree with experimental measurements within 15% across all 5 operating points.",
      "rationale": "CFD-predicted normalized index of hemolysis (NIH) compared against experimental NIH measurements across all 5 operating conditions. Maximum deviation 11.3%, mean deviation 7.6%, satisfying the 15% acceptance criterion."
