      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "The QoI (relative hemolysis index RH) directly maps to the clinical decision criterion and is computed consistently between simulation and experiment.",
      "rationale": "The relative hemolysis index RH = NIH_device / NIH_predicate is the direct regulatory acceptance metric. Both CFD and experimental pipelines compute NIH using the ASTM F1841 power-law model, ensuring QoI consistency."
